    "text": "The system integrates soil moisture, TDS (Total Dissolved Solids), and DHT11 (temperature and humidity) sensors to continuously monitor soil and environmental parameters in real time.",
    "topic": "IoT Soil Monitoring System"
  },
  {
    "text": "ESP32 microcontrollers are used in the IoT-based smart soil regeneration tracking system.",
    "topic": "IoT Hardware"
  },
  {
    "text": "The system is designed to track soil regeneration in real-time using IoT technology.",
    "topic": "Real-Time Soil Monitoring"
  },
  {
    "text": "AI-based soil nutrient prediction is integrated into the system for future crop recommendation.",
    "topic": "AI Soil Nutrient Prediction"
  },
  {
    "text": "The system includes automated soil rejuvenation control based on the collected data and AI predictions.",
    "topic": "Automated Soil Rejuvenation"
  }
